<sect1 id="dir_c06739a7e81ea970219d6849a6b58298_1autotoc_md213">
<title>GameState</title><para>Bitmask enum with values:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>Undefined</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Loading</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Title</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Menu</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Paused</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Running</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Any</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Supports bitwise operators for combining states.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_c06739a7e81ea970219d6849a6b58298_1autotoc_md214">
<title>GameStateTransitionRule</title><para>Defines a valid transition with:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Source state (<computeroutput>from</computeroutput>)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Transition identifier (<computeroutput>transitionId</computeroutput>)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Target state (<computeroutput>to</computeroutput>)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Transition type</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Optional guard callback</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
